body:
Hi there, so if you want to contact me, feel free to do so on twitter or facebook.
ALso you can write an email if you'd like to.

And by feel free, I mean it. Raccoons love people.

Website is powered by Phenomic, so if you feel like something's missing or you just saw something wrong, please contribute to make this blog better by raising an issue on GitHub!
